highlights.text: Vestavind has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Ligga” is the highest at #1.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 68 days straight.
“Waterfalls (feat. Sam Harper & Bobby Harvey)” by James Hype, Sam Harper, and Bobby Harvey is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #92.
“i don’t want your garden” by Hazlett is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 18 spots at #70.
